The '''''Red Nova''''' was a [[Pirate/Legends|pirate]] [[Cruiser/Legends|cruiser]] affiliated with the [[Invids]]. When based on [[Courkrus]] in [[11 ABY/Legends|11 ABY]], its crew congregated in a [[Cantina/Legends|cantina]] called the Warren, along with [[Riistar's Raiders]]. The [[Bulk cruiser/Legends|bulk cruiser]] ''[[Booty Full]]'' was also once affiliated with the ''Red Nova'' crew. Though the ''Red Nova'' crew was never specifically targeted by [[Corran Horn/Legends|Corran Horn]] in his "Ghost [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]]" guise, fear of the Jedi caused their ranks to be decimated by desertion. The remaining crew began negotiating with the [[LazerLords]] to merge their gangs, as neither had enough remaining members to adequately function alone.

